---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Industries &mdash; Forge T Labs"
  description="The industries Forge T Labs serves across Dynamics 365, Modern Work and Azure."
  canonical=""
  ogType="website"
  active="Industries"
>
<main id="top">
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; Industries</div>
    <h1>Industries we <em>serve</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Our Microsoft Cloud expertise &mdash; Dynamics 365, Modern Work, Azure and AI &mdash; applies across many industries. We go deepest in real estate and construction, the sector our own product suite is built for.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <span class="mono">Where we work</span>
      <h2>Microsoft Cloud expertise, <em>applied to your sector</em>.</h2>
      <p>Every industry has its own systems, data and compliance realities. We bring the same
        certified Microsoft platform skill to each &mdash; and the deepest specialisation where
        we have built our own software.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ind-grid">
      <article class="ind reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M3 21h18M6 21V8l6-4 6 4v13"/><path d="M10 21v-5h4v5" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Real Estate &amp; Construction</h3>
        <p>Our anchor industry. From construction project delivery to property operations and portfolio management &mdash; and the sector our Forge product suite is built for.</p>
        <span class="tag">Flagship focus</span>
      </article>
      <article class="ind reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><circle cx="9" cy="20" r="1.5"/><circle cx="18" cy="20" r="1.5"/><path d="M2 3h3l2.5 12h11l2-8H6" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Professional Services</h3>
        <p>Project-based firms &mdash; consultancies, agencies, engineering practices &mdash; that run on accurate project, resource and client data.</p>
        <span class="tag">Dynamics 365</span>
      </article>
      <article class="ind reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M3 21h18M3 21V10l6 4V10l6 4V6l6 3v12" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Manufacturing &amp; Distribution</h3>
        <p>Operations, inventory and field service teams modernising on Business Central and connected cloud systems.</p>
        <span class="tag">D365 &middot; Azure</span>
      </article>
      <article class="ind reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 20s-7-4.5-7-10a4 4 0 0 1 7-2.5A4 4 0 0 1 19 10c0 5.5-7 10-7 10Z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Healthcare &amp; Life Sciences</h3>
        <p>Patient-facing and back-office teams that need secure, compliant collaboration and data on the Microsoft Cloud.</p>
        <span class="tag">Modern Work</span>
      </article>
      <article class="ind reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M3 21h18M5 21V9m14 12V9M3 9l9-5 9 5M9 21v-7h6v7"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Financial Services</h3>
        <p>Firms with strict security and compliance needs adopting Microsoft 365 and Azure with the right governance baked in.</p>
        <span class="tag">Security</span>
      </article>
      <article class="ind reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M4 5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h13v15H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2V5Z"/><path d="M4 19a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h13" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Education</h3>
        <p>Institutions rolling out modern collaboration, identity and device management for staff and students.</p>
        <span class="tag">Modern Work</span>
      </article>
      <article class="ind reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M3 21h18M5 21v-9m4 9v-9m6 9v-9m4 9v-9M3 12l9-7 9 7"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Government &amp; Public Sector</h3>
        <p>Agencies modernising legacy systems and citizen-facing services on a secure, compliant cloud foundation.</p>
        <span class="tag">Azure &middot; D365</span>
      </article>
      <article class="ind reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 20s-7-4.5-7-10a4 4 0 0 1 7-2.5A4 4 0 0 1 19 10c0 5.5-7 10-7 10Z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Nonprofit</h3>
        <p>Mission-driven organisations getting more from constrained budgets with the Microsoft Cloud and AI.</p>
        <span class="tag">Modern Work</span>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="band">
  <div class="wrap isv">
    <div class="isv-copy reveal">
      <span class="mono" style="color:var(--green);display:block;margin-bottom:16px">Our deepest specialisation</span>
      <h2>Real estate &amp; construction.</h2>
      <p>It is the industry we know best &mdash; and the one we committed to as a software builder.
        The Forge product suite covers the full life of a commercial building: design and fit-out,
        construction, property operations, and portfolio management.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:14px">For real estate and construction clients, that means a partner
        who understands the work, not just the platform.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions" style="margin-top:28px">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/solutions">Explore the Forge suite &rarr;</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/contact">Talk to us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tiers reveal">
      <div class="tier"><div><div class="tname">SpecForge</div>
        <div class="tdesc">Workplace design &amp; fit-out</div></div></div>
      <div class="tier featured"><div><span class="badge">Lead product</span>
        <div class="tname">BuildForge</div>
        <div class="tdesc">Construction project management</div></div></div>
      <div class="tier"><div><div class="tname">SiteForge</div>
        <div class="tdesc">Property operations</div></div></div>
      <div class="tier"><div><div class="tname">AssetForge</div>
        <div class="tdesc">CRE portfolio tracking</div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cta-band reveal">
      <div class="glow"></div>
      <h2>Don't see your industry?</h2>
      <p>Our Microsoft Cloud services are not industry-bound. If your organisation runs on
        Microsoft &mdash; or should &mdash; we can help. Tell us what you are working on.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Start a conversation &rarr;</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/services">See our services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
